Advisory Council was formed. The purpose of this
council is to ascertain what is needed in the way of
courses, equipment, and buildings, so that the Pitt
Engineer will need less industrial orientation than
ever before. The council will also assist the Trustees
Committee in developing support to supply the pre-
determined needs.
